You don't usually think of west africa as a surf spot, but we went out a few days because we heard there was a local scene... "I want to surf this wave no more" in a thick west african accent is what the local Ghanaian kid joshua said to me after a few hours of surfing. the wave wasnt big but he mastered it.. he was raised in a fishing village and fostered by a local surf shop outpost called @mr.brights.surfing.ghana and now he's the best surfer in Ghana.. even tho most the local kids learned to surf on homemade wood plans with nailed on fins .. they learned quick and spend every morning on the water. it reminds me of growing up with the small waves in florida and just dreaming about getting ou one day .. joshua eventually got a proper board and became one of the best raw talent surfers i've ever seen but he doesn't even have a smart phone to know that i'm posting about him.. swipe left to see about the amazing board drive for the local talent and take a chance and go surf in Africa when you visit . I still suck at surfing ..

I know you guys are probably familiar with crystals and know the amazing healing powers that they can bring.. but I have something better for you.. Potatoes!! after traveling all over the planet and attending wellness retreats and making  research with the some of the top scientists i have been  astounded by the results . I even started to sleep with my potato and carrying it in a special potato sack while i perform around the globe .. potatoes promote good flow of your chi and help rid your mind body and soul of bad negative energy, .. this picture is a yam I found in africa, it is considered a master healer and helps reduce anxiety, removes emotional blocks and makes me more fertile. It's insane that have spent my whole life without a potato in my pocket and now i'm in awe of the results .. there are many varieties such as russet potatoes, sweet potatoes, fingerlings, yams and also cassavas. I can answer questions in the comments and will be doing speaking engagements to teach the power of potatos all through 2020 .. it's a new year let's cleanse your mind and body of bad juju and remember  you can purchase tater tot necklaces in my bio and at my shows . #cowboy #potato #africa #wellness #energy ..
